20angle%20of%20the%20alleged%20scam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20is%20probing%20the%20money%20laundering%20angle%20of%20the%20alleged%20scam%20and%20this%20is%20the%20eighth%20chargesheet%20it%20has%20filed%20in%20the%20case%2C%20but%20the%20first%20in%20which%20the%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20has%20been%20named.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20on%20March%2021%2C%20becoming%20the%20third%20senior%20AAP%20leader%20to%20be%20taken%20into%20custody%20in%20the%20alleged%20scam%2C%20after%20his%20former%20deputy%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20decision%20to%20name%20the%20AAP%20as%20an%20accused%20can%20have%20major%20repercussions%20for%20the%20party.%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20they%20said%2C%20now%20has%20the%20option%20of%20writing%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20and%20requesting%20them%20to%20begin%20the%20process%20of%20derecognising%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party.%20It%20can%20also%20attach%20the%20party's%20assets%2C%20including%20its%20headquarters%20in%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20AAP%20finds%20itself%20embroiled%20in%20a%20controversy%20surrounding%20its%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Swati%20Maliwal%2C%20who%20has%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20slapped%20and%20kicked%20by%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20aide%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20at%20the%20chief%20minister's%20residence%20on%20Monday%2C%20when%20she%20was%20waiting%20to%20meet%20the%20AAP%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20have%20kicked%20up%20a%20political%20storm%20and%20the%20AAP%20has%20faced%20attacks%20from%20various%20quarters%2C%20including%20from%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman.%20An%20alleged%20video%20from%20the%20day%20has%20also%20led%20to%20Ms%20Maliwal%20and%20the%20AAP%20trading%20charges.%20Earlier%20on%20Friday%2C%20a%20Delhi%20Police%20team%2C%20accompanied%20by%20forensic%20specialists%2C%20had%20visit