id%20the%20way%20the%20project%20in%20Jaipur's%20upmarket%20area%20of%20Gandhinagar%20-%20which%20is%20home%20to%20senior%20judges%20and%20IAS%20officers%20among%20others%20-%20is%20being%20planned%20will%20result%20in%20a%20loss%20of%20Rs%201%2C146%20crore%20to%20the%20state%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Meena%20has%20also%20said%20that%20the%20General%20Administration%20Department%20(GAD)%2C%20which%20is%20under%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20is%20going%20ahead%20with%20the%20project%20without%20cabinet%20clearance%20and%20has%20urged%20Mr%20Sharma%20to%20stop%20it%20and%20recall%20the%20file.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumbers%20Game%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20Mr%20Meena%20speaks%20about%20the%20planned%20redevelopment%20of%20the%20old%20MREC%20campus%20In%20Gandhinagar%2C%20where%20the%20GAD%20plans%20to%20demolish%20existing%20buildings%20and%20build%20multi-storey%20towers.%20The%20minister%20has%20said%20the%20area%20was%20valued%20at%20Rs%20277%20crore%20five%20years%20ago%20and%20a%20new%20assessment%20has%20put%20its%20value%20at%20Rs%20218%20crore.%20The%20reserve%20price%20of%20the%20land%2C%20he%20claims%2C%20is%20also%20undervalued%20at%20Rs%208%2C000%20per%20square%20foot%20against%20the%20current%20rate%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%2C%20according%20to%20the%20letter%2C%20that%20the%20state%20government%20is%20incurring%20a%20loss%20of%20nearly%20Rs%2017%2C000%20per%20square%20foot.%20The%20government%20is%20also%20planning%20to%20give%20nearly%2033%25%20-%20or%20a%20third%20-%20of%20the%20flats%20to%20private%20players%20as%20part%20of%20a%20public-private%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20these%2C%20Mr%20Meena%20said%2C%20add%20up%20to%20a%20loss%20of%201%2C146%20crore%20to%20the%20state%20treasury.%20Claiming%20that%20the%20file%20for%20the%20project%20has%20not%20been%20cleared%20by%20the%20cabinet%20or%20the%20finance%20ministry%2C%20the%20minister%20has