0to%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20by%20July%2C%20reports%20said.%20The%20LCA%20Tejas%20MK1A%2C%20the%20advanced%20version%20of%20the%20MK1%2C%20conducted%20its%20first%20successful%20test%20flight%20on%20March%2028%20this%20year%2C%20marking%20a%20historic%20moment%20in%20India's%20fighter%20jet%20development%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Light%20Combat%20Aircraft%20(LCA)%20programme%20was%20envisioned%20in%20the%20late%201980s%20to%20replace%20the%20MiG-21s%20and%20Su-7s%20fleet.%20The%20programme%20got%20a%20boost%20in%20the%20late%2090s.%20On%20January%204%2C%202001%2C%20the%20Technology%20Demonstrator-1%20(TD-1)%20version%20of%20the%20LCA%20was%20airborne%20and%20rechristened%20as%20'Tejas'%2C%20a%20significant%20moment%20in%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Second%20Series%20Production%20(SP2)%20Tejas%20aircraft%20was%20given%20initial%20operational%20clearance%20in%202016.%20The%20Tejas%20MK1%20version%20was%20inducted%20in%20the%20Air%20Force's%20No.%2045%20Squadron%20-%20'The%20Flying%20Daggers'.%20Later%2C%20another%20Tejas%20squadron%2C%20No.%2018%20Squadron%20-%20'The%20Flying%20Bullets'%20began%20operating%20the%20MK1%20variant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Is%20Tejas%20MK1A%20Different%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20has%20ordered%2083%20Tejas%20MK1A%20variants%20in%20a%20Rs%2036%2C468%20crore%20deal%20with%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Limited.%20In%20November%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Defence%20Acquisition%20Council%20cleared%20the%20project%20to%20acquire%2097%20more%20Tejas%20jets%20for%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F1st-flight-of-light-combat-aircraft-tejas-mk1a-conducted-successfully-5327131%5C%22%3EOn%20March%2028%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Group%20Captain%20K%20K%20Venugopal%20(Retired)%2C%20a%20test%20pilot%2C%20took%20the%20Tejas%20MK1A%20to%20the%20skies%20and%20was%20airborne%20for%2015%20minutes.%20The%20sortie%20was%20the%20first%20successful%20flight%20of%20the%20MK1A%20version%20of%20the%20fighter%20jet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGroup%20Captain%20Sunit%20Krishna%2C%20a%20test%20pilot%20of%20the%20LCA%20Tejas%20MK1%2C%20spoke%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3iB1hVo4Gd0%26t%3D128s%5C%22%3ENDTV%20India%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWith%20time%2C%20the%20technology%20has%20to%20be%20improved%20and%20have%20to%20be%20integrated.%20The%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20wanted%20new%20systems%20to%20be%20integrated%20into%20the%20Tejas%20so%20that%20it%20could%20be%20in%20service%20for%20the%20next%20three%20decades.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20aircraft%20might%20look%20similar%20from%20the%20outside%2C%20but%20new%20electronics%2C%20processors%2C%20display%20systems%2C%20and%20the%20hardware%20of%20fly-by-wire%20systems%20have%20been%20integrated...To%20list%20out%2C%20it%20has%20new%20AESA%20radar%2C%20air-to-ground%2C%20air-to-air%20modes%20and%20self-protection%20jammers%2C%20and%20the%20mission%20computer%20in%20MK1A%20is%20new%20and%20indigenous.%20The%20aircraft%20is%20future-ready%2C%26quot%3B%20Group%20Captain%20Krishna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20design%20of%20an%20aircraft%20poses%20limitations%20to%20integrating%20new%20systems.%20The%20HAL%20has%20incorporated%20the%20latest%20technology%20with%20slight%20modifications%20in%20the%20design%20to%20give%20a%20newer%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20variant%20will%20have%20almost%2050%20per%20cent%20more%20indigenous%20content%20than%20its%20predecessor.%20The%20MK1A%20version%20will%20have%2040%20more%20improvements%20than%20the%20previous%20one.%20The%20Tejas%20MK1A%20will%20have%20the%20advanced%20Israel%20EL%2FM-2025%20AESA%20(Active%20Electronically%20Scanned%20Array)%20Radar.%20It%20will%20soon%20be%20replaced%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drdo.gov.in%2Fdrdo%2Flabs-establishment%2Ftechnologies%2Felectronics-radar-development-establishment-lrde%5C%22%3EUttam%20AESA%20Radar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20indigenously%20developed%20by%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Limited%20and%20the%20HAL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Uttam%20is%20a%20fully%20engineered%2C%20qualified%20and%20deployable%20radar%20%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Uttam%20is%20a%20fully%20engineered%2C%20qualified%20and%20deployable%20radar%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fb7m5apog_uttam-aesa-radar_625x300_17_May_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttam%20is%20a%20fully%20engineered%2C%20qualified%20and%20deployable%20radar%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttam%20Radar%20can%20track%20multiple%20targets%20and%20reportedly%20has%20a%20range%20of%20more%20than%20200%20km%20to%20give%20the%20aircraft%20a%20360-degree%20scanned%20view%20of%20its%20surroundings.%20It%20will%20be%20used%20in%20the%20later%20variants%20like%20Tejas%20MK2%20and%20the%20Twin%20Engine%20Deck-Based%20Fighters%20(TEDBF).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20HAL%20has%20maintained%20a%20commonality%20between%20the%20MK1%20and%20MK1A%20variants.%20The%20new%20version%20will%20have%20enhanced%20situational%20awareness%20with%20a%20slightly%20bigger%20canopy%20and%20changes%20in%20the%20jet%20aerodynamics%20to%20improve%20its%20manoeuvrability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMK1A%20will%20have%20around%20nine%20hard%20points%20on%20its%20underbelly%20to%20carry%20various%20types%20of%20weaponry%20like%20the%20Beyond%20Visual%20Range%20(BVR)%20missiles%2C%20Air-to-Air%2FGround%20missiles%2C%20and%20Advanced%20Short%20Range%20Air-to-Air%20missiles%20(ASRAAM).%20External%20self-protection%20jammer%20pods%20will%20allow%20the%20aircraft%20to%20engage%20in%20electronic%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20indigenously%20developed%20digital%20fly-by-wire%20flight%20control%20computer%20was%20integrated%20into%20the%20Tejas%20jet.%20A%20Fly-by-wire%20systems%20in%20aircraft%20flight%20control%20systems%20replace%20mechanical%20flight%20controls%20with%20an%20electronic%20interface%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20significant%20development%20towards%20Tejas%20Mk1A%20programme%2C%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftejas-jet-flies-successfully-with-india-made-digital-flight-control-system-5094608%5C%22%3E%20digital%20fly-by-wire%20flight%20control%20computer%3C%2Fa%3E%20(DFCC)%20was%20integrated%20into%20prototype%20LSP7%20and%20successfully%20flown%20on%20February%2019%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20defence%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Tejas%20Mk1A%20will%20have%20an%20advanced%20electronic%20RADAR%2C%20warfare%20and%20communication%20systems%2C%20additional%20combat%20capability%20and%20improved%20maintenance%20features%2C%26quot%3B%20HAL%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Electronic%20Warfare%20Suite%20consists%20of%20a%20Radar%20Warning%20Receiver%20(RWR)%20system%20%26amp%3B%20Advanced%20Self%20Protection%20Jammer%20(ASPJ)%20pod%20will%20be%20installed%20into%20MK1A.%C2%A0The%20purpose%20of%20the%20system%20is%20to%20protect%20the%20aircraft%20against%20ground-based%20acquisition%20radars%2C%20fire%20control%20radars%2C%20anti-aircraft%20artillery%20and%20airborne%20multimode%20radars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETejas%20-%20Lightest%2C%20Smallest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejas%20is%20the%20smallest%20and%20lightest%20aircraft%20in%20its%20class%20and%20the%20dimensions%20and%20the%20extensive%20use%20of%20composite%20structure%20make%20it%20lighter.%20The%204.5%20generation%20aircraft%20can%20be%20used%20for%20multiple%20roles%20like%20ground%20attack%2C%20interception%2C%20air-to-air%20combat%20and%20air%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20force%20plans%20to%20raise%20the%20first%20squadron%20of%20the%20indigenous%20LCA%20Mark1A%20fighter%20aircraft%20squadron%20at%20the%20Nal%20air%20base%20in%20the%20Bikaner%20district%20of%20Rajasthan%20near%20the%20Pakistan%20front.%20The%20Tejas%20will%20replace%20one%20of%20the%20two%20MiG-21%20squadrons%20already%20stationed%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffirst-lca-mark-1a-fighter-aircraft-squadron-to-be-deployed-at-rajasthans-nal-air-base-4651386%5C%22%3EANI%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tejas%20MK1%2C%20MK1A%2C%20and%20MK2%20variants%20will%20replace%20the%20MiG21%2C%20MiG-29%2C%20and%20SEPECAT%20Jaguar%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2023%20years%20of%20its%20history%20since%20the%20first%20test%20flight%20in%202001%2C%20the%20Tejas%20aircraft%20has%20maintained%20an%20excellent%20flight%20safety%20record.%20In%20March%2C%20a%20Tejas%20from%20the%20No.18%20squadron%20crashed%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20but%20it%20was%20the%20first%20such%20instance%20in%2023%20years%20of%20its%20history%20and%20almost%20eight%20years%20of%20operational%20deployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENigeria%2C%20Philippines%2C%20Argentina%20and%20Egypt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fphilippines-argentina-egypt-interested-in-procuring-tejas-jet-hal-chief-cb-ananthakrishnan-4642069%5C%22%3Ehave%20shown%20interest%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20procuring%20indigenously-developed%20Tejas%20Light%20Combat%20Aircraft%2C%20CB%20Ananthakrishnan%2C%20the%20Chairman%20and%20Managing%20Director%20of%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Ltd%2C%20earlier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715949360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fc921tht8_lca-tejas-mk1a-ani_625x300_28_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-new-tejas-fighter-jet-variant-is-different-from-its-predecessor-5685154%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20upgraded%20version%20of%20the%20indigenous%20supersonic%20fighter%20aircraft%2C%20the%20Tejas%20MK1A%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20delivered%20to%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20by%20July%2C%20reports%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%2