%20a%20long-buried%2064-kilometre-long%20river%20branch%20of%20the%20Nile%20River.%20It%20was%20hidden%20under%20desert%20and%20farmland%20for%20millennia%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20by%20the%20University%20of%20North%20Carolina%20Wilmington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20added%20the%20river%20branch%20used%20to%20flow%20alongside%20the%2031%20pyramids%20in%20Egypt.%20It%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20river%20was%20used%20to%20transport%20giant%20stone%20blocks.%20The%20latest%20discovery%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20has%20also%20explained%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20construction%20of%20pyramids%20in%20a%20chain%20between%204%2C700%20and%203%2C700%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadar%20satellite%20imagery%20was%20used%20by%20researchers%20to%20map%20the%20river%20branch.%20Eman%20Ghoneim%2C%20the%20University%20of%20North%20Carolina%20Wilmington%20earth%20and%20ocean%20sciences%20professor%2C%20told%20the%20news%20agency%20AFP%20that%20the%20radar%20gave%20them%20the%20%26quot%3Bunique%20ability%20to%20penetrate%20the%20sand%20surface%20and%20produce%20images%20of%20hidden%20features%20including%20buried%20rivers%20and%20ancient%20structures.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Funcw.edu%2Fnews%2F2024%2F05%2Fresearchers-uncover-buried-branch-of-nile-river%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20by%20the%20university%2C%20the%20team%20also%20%E2%80%9Cfound%20many%20of%20the%20pyramids%20had%20causeways%20that%20ended%20at%20the%20proposed%20riverbanks%20of%20the%20Ahramat%20branch%2C%20which%20they%20suggest%20is%20evidence%20the%20river%20was%20used%20for%20transporting%20construction%20materials.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20study%2C%20Eman%20Ghoneim%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20us%20who%20are%20interested%20in%20ancient%20Egypt%20are%20aware%20that%20the%20Egyptians%20must%20have%20used%20a%20waterway%20to%20build%20their%20enormous%20monuments%2C%20like%20the%20pyramids%20and%20valley%20temples%2C%20but%20nobody%20was%20certain%20of%20the%20location%2C%20the%20shape%2C%20the%20size%2C%20or%20proximity%20of%20this%20mega%20waterway%20to%20the%20actual%20pyramids%20site.%20Our%20research%20offers%20the%20first%20map%20of%20one%20of%20the%20main%20ancient%20branches%20of%20the%20Nile%20at%20such%20a%20large%20scale%20and%20links%20it%20with%20the%20largest%20pyramid%20fields%20of%20Egypt.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20were%20published%20in%20the%20research%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs43247-024-01379-7%5C%22%3ECommunications%20Earth%20%26amp%3B%20Environment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715944440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fev3p5jbs_giza-pyramid_625x300_17_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmystery-of-how-egyptians-built-pyramids-may-have-been-solved-5684214%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20group%20of%20researchers%20has%20finally%20found%20a%20long-buried%2064-kilometre-long%20river%20branch%20of%20the%20Nile%20River.%20It%20was%20hidden%20under%20desert%20and%20farmland%20for%20millennia%2C%20according%20to%20a%20study%20by%20the%20University%20of%20North%20Carolina%20Wilmington.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmystery-of-how-egyptians-built-pyramids-may-have-been-solved-5684214%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmystery-of-how-egyptians-built-pyramids-may-have-been-solved-5684214%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmystery-of-how-egyptians-built-pyramids-may-have-been-solved-5684214%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20PM%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20Wife%20Akshata%20Murty's%20Wealth%20Soars%20In%202024%20Rich%20List%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBritish%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20and%20wife%20Akshata%20Murty%2C%20who%20made%20their%20debut%20in%20the%20annual%20'Sunday%20Times%20Rich%20List'%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20have%20moved%20up%20the%20ranks%20in%20the%202024%20edition%20released%20on%20Friday%20thanks%20to%20the%20Akshata%20Murty's%20lucrative%20Infosys%20shareholding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%2C%20both%2044%2C%20have%20risen%20from%20275th%20last%20year%20to%20245th%20with%20an%20estimated%20wealth%20of%20GBP%20651%20million%2C%20making%20them%20the%20%26quot%3Bwealthiest%20people%20to%20call%2010%20Downing%20Street%20home%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshata%20Murty's%20earnings%20are%20said%20to%20far%20exceed%20that%20of%20her%20husband%20as%20financial%20statements%20published%20in%20February%20are%20quoted%20to%20say%20Rishi%20Sunak%20made%20GBP%202.2%20million%20in%202022-23%20compared%20to%20AkshataMurty's%20estimated%20GBP%2013%20million%20in%20dividends%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20couple's%20most%20valued%20asset%20is%20Akshata%20Murty's%20shareholding%20in%20Infosys%2C%20a%20Bangalore-based%20IT%20company%20co-founded%20by%20Akshata%20Murty's%20father%20%5BNarayan%20Murthy%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20the%20newspaper's%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%20year%2C%20the%20shares%20have%20grown%20in%20value%20by%20GBP%20108.8%20million%20to%20nearly%20GBP%20590%20million.%20The%20latest%20annual%20report%20suggests%20that%20Murty%20received%20about%20GBP%2013%20million%20in%20dividends%20during%20that%20time%20-%20adding%20to%20the%20more%20than%20a%20million%20pounds%20she%20has%20been%20paid%20in%20previous%20years.%20She%20is%20poised%20to%20receive%20another%20GBP%2010.5%20million%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20compilation%20of%20Britain's%20wealthiest%20families%20is%20once%20again%20topped%20by%20the%20Indian-origin%20Hinduja%20family%2C%20who%20saw%20their%20wealth%20increase%20over%20the%20past%20year%20to%20hit%20GBP%2037.196%20billion%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20opening%20of%20their%20brand-new%20luxury%20OWO%20Hotel%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK-based%20family's%20group%20of%20companies%2C%20headed%20by%20chairman%20G.P.%20Hinduja%2C%20operates%20in%2048%20countries%20and%20across%20several%20sectors%20-%20automotive%2C%20oil%20and%20speciality%20chemicals%2C%20banking%20and%20finance%2C%20IT%2C%20cyber%20security%2C%20healthcare%2C%20trading%2C%20infrastructure%20project%20development%2C%20media%20and%20entertainment%2C%20power%2C%20and%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20a%20year%20of%20expansion%20through%20acquisition%20for%20the%20group%2C%20made%20possible%20in%20part%20by%20growing%20stock%20market%20valuations%20of%20the%20family's%20main%20listed%20holdings%2C%20which%20have%20risen%20to%20a%20total%20of%20GBP%208.7%20billion%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20the%20newspaper's%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%2010%20of%20the%202024%20'Sunday%20Times%20Rich%20List'%20sees%20another%20set%20of%20India-born%20brothers%2C%20David%20and%20Simon%20Reuben%2C%20build%20on%20their%20wealth%20to%20rise%20to%20third%20place%20from%20last%20year's%20fourth%2C%20with%20a%20fortune%20estimated%20at%20around%20GBP%2024.977%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20No.%208%20is%20NRI%20tycoon%20of%20ArcelorMittal%20steelworks%20Lakshmi%20N.%20Mittal%2C%20who%20slips%20two%20places%20from%20last%20year%20with%20an%20estimated%20GBP%2014.921%20billion%2C%20followed%20by%20Vedanta%20Resources'%20industrialist%20Anil%20Agarwal%20at%20No.%2023%20with%20an%20estimated%20GBP%207%20billion%20-%20down%20one%20rank%20from%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20Indian-origin%20billionaires%20on%20the%202024%20list%20include%20textiles%20entrepreneur%20Prakash%20Lohia%20at%20No.%2030%20with%20an%20estimated%20GBP%206.23%20billion%3B%20retail%20majors%20Mohsin%20and%20Zuber%20Issa%20at%20No.%2039%20with%20GBP%205%20billion%3B%20and%20pharma%20chiefs%20Navin%20and%20Varsha%20Engineer%20at%2058%20with%20GBP%203%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20top%20100%20richest%20Britons%20are%20brothers%20Simon%2C%20Bobby%20and%20Robin%20Arora%20at%20No.%2065%20with%20GBP%202.682%20billion%20and%20leading%20NRI%20industrialist%20Lord%20Swraj%20Paul%20and%20family%20ranked%2067th%20with%20an%20estimated%20wealth%20of%20GBP%202.6%20billion%20-%20same%20as%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFashion%20industrialist%20Sunder%20Genomal%2C%20a%20new%20entrant%20in%202023%2C%20is%20ranked%2077th%20with%20a%20fortune%20estimated%20at%20GBP%202.214%20billion%2C%20with%20hoteliers%20Jasminder%20Singh%20and%20family%20coming%20in%20at%2083%20with%20GBP%202.001%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20whole%2C%20the%2036th%20edition%20of%20the%20rich%20list%20reveals%20the%20largest%20fall%20in%20billionaires%20in%20its%20history%20-%20down%20from%20a%20peak%20of%20177%20in%202022%20to%20165%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20year's%20Sunday%20Times%20Rich%20List%20suggests%20Britain's%20billionaire%20boom%20has%20come%20to%20an%20end.%20Many%20of%20our%20home-grown%20entrepreneurs%20have%20seen%20their%20fortunes%20fall%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20global%20super-rich%20who%20came%20here%20are%20moving%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20list's%20compiler%2C%20Robert%20Watts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20moving%20from%20millionaire%20to%20billionaire%20on%20the%20tally%20is%20former%20Beatle%20Sir%20Paul%20McCartney%20-%20now%20the%20first%20UK%20musician%20to%20achieve%20that%20status%20after%20boosting%20his%20wealth%20by%20GBP%2050%20million%20over%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715943780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F4rs0v53g_akshata-murt